83 "SECTION 17.
84 Subject to appropriation of funds by the commissioners, the board shall be authorized to
85 expend county funds to provide for such proper and suitable administrative offices and for
86 such clerical assistance and other employees as the board shall deem appropriate.
87 Compensation for such administrative personnel shall be paid by the board under the
88 county personnel system wholly from county funds. This section shall not be construed
89 so as to require the board to expend any funds simply because they are authorized to do so
90 under this Act. Employees of the board shall be considered county employees for pay,
91 benefits, sick leave, vacation, and for other purposes, and such pay shall be as determined
92 by the governing authority of the county."
93 SECTION 6.
94 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
